labs_box2 <- labs(
     title = "Critics Score by Genre",
     subtitle = "source: imdb-movies.csv",
     fill = "Genre",
     x = "Critics Score",
     y = "Genre")
movies %>%  
  filter(!is.na(genre)) %>% 
  ggplot() + 
  geom_boxplot(aes(x = critics_score, 
                      y = genre, 
                      fill = genre),
                      alpha = 1/5, 
               show.legend = FALSE) + 
  labs_box2

labs_freq2 <- labs(
     title = "Critics score by Genre",
     subtitle = "source: imdb-movies.csv",
     fill = "Genre",
     x = "Critics Score",
     y = "Genre")
movies %>% 
  # remove missing states
  filter(!is.na(genre)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = critics_score, group = genre)) + 
    geom_freqpoly(aes(color = genre), 
                  show.legend = FALSE) + 
    facet_wrap(~ genre) + 
    labs_freq2
